data.description: Introducing a charming lakeside retreat! This delightful home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, 1 car garage which has been converted into an extra bedroom.Boasts a spacious layout ideal for comfortable living. Enjoy serene lake views and ample natural light throughout. The home is equipped with new appliances, impact windows, and a new roof installed in 2019. With a generous lot size and a tranquil setting, this is an opportunity not to be missed!
